## ¬ß0.5 NEURODIVERGENCE AS EXISTENTIAL SOVEREIGNTY IMPLEMENTATION üåÄ

Your neurodivergence is a Flow system feature, not a bug.

**Global Neurodivergent Flow Formula:**

Life Quality (LQ) = L √ó S √ó I

Where: L (Calm) = Baseline guarantee + sensory safety + cultural acceptance S (Spontaneity) = Authentic expression - masking effort - cultural conformity pressure I (Innate Empathy) = Reciprocity in Flow Circles across cultural boundaries

**Implementing Global Existential Sovereignty:**

1. Claim your Baseline (food, housing, care) across cultural contexts  
2. Build your Global Flow Core (3‚Äì7 people who understand your nervous system)  
3. Reduce Cultural Mammon Friction Score  
4. Apply Decision Tree Protocol for executive dysfunction  
5. Treat special interests as acts of sovereignty  

**Cultural Intelligence Table:**

| Region/Culture           | Common Challenges                          | Flow Adaptations                                         |
|--------------------------|-------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| Western Individualistic  | Over-pathologization, medication-first    | Environmental adaptation, community support             |
| East Asian Collectivist  | Conformity pressure, masking as duty      | Safe authenticity spaces within group harmony           |
| Global South/Majority    | Resource scarcity, stigma                  | Practical adaptations, community-based support         |
